Class Ecountry

  • java.lang.Object
    • Ecountry

  • public class Ecountry
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by John on 5/15/14. Class Description: Basic template for countries read from the Countries.txt file. Stores 5 basic variables: Country name, capital name, region name region number, and capital population.
